OL,4,Ctenor during live show
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Royal Ballet &
OL,7,FOpera (RBO) said on Wednesday:
OL,8,F"Roberto Alagna was taken unwell
OL,9,Fduring yesterday evening's performance
OL,10,Fof Turandot, which prevented him from
OL,11,Fcompleting Act III. We wish Roberto a
OL,12,Fswift and full recovery."
OL,14,FOne X user described it as a "poor
OL,15,Fshow", criticising the Royal Opera
OL,16,FHouse for not having a replacement
OL,17,Fperformer available.
OL,19,FOther audience members were more
OL,20,Fsympathetic.
