OL,3,CRoyal Opera conductor replaces sick
OL,4,Ctenor during live show
OL,6,FWriter Kenan Malik took to X to
OL,7,Fexpress his mixed feelings.
OL,9,F"Drama at the opera tonight," he
OL,10,Fwrote. "During Turandot at Covent
OL,11,FGarden, Roberto Alagna, playing Calaf,
OL,12,Ftook ill and couldn't come out for Act
OL,13,FIII. So, Richard Hetherington, ROH's
OL,14,Fhead of music, but not a trained opera
OL,15,Fsinger, gamely stepped in, to sing
OL,16,Ffrom the side.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
