OL,3,CRoyal Opera conductor replaces sick
OL,4,Ctenor during live show
OL,6,F"But he couldn't sing the main arias
OL,7,For duets. So, they began Act III after
OL,8,FNessun Dorma. And ended before the
OL,9,Ffinal scenes, finishing at the point
OL,10,Fwhere Liu takes her life rather than
OL,11,Freveal Calaf's name.
OL,13,F"So, disappointing, dramatic and a
OL,14,Fstrangely appropriate ending all at
OL,15,Fthe same time. And hugely brave and
OL,16,Fimpressive of Hetherington to step in."
