OL,6,FThe RBO told ITV News: "Calaf is a
OL,7,Frole of extraordinary vocal demand. It
OL,8,Fis not the type of role for which a
OL,9,Fcover typically stands by during every
OL,10,Fperformance.
OL,12,F"This is a standard practice across
OL,13,Fmajor opera houses internationally,
OL,14,Fdue to the specialist nature of the
OL,15,Fpart and the rarity of singers who can
OL,16,Fperform it at this level."
OL,18,FCustomers have since been credited 50
OL,19,Fper cent of the ticket price as a
OL,20,Fresult of the impact to the
OL,21,Fperformance.
